  "type": "skill",
  "description": "Systematic refactoring using proven techniques",
  "longDescription": "Covers six categories with step-by-step mechanics: Composing Methods (Extract Method, Inline Temp, etc.), Moving Features (Move Method/Field, Extract/Inline Class), Organizing Data (Encapsulate Field, Replace Type Code), Simplifying Conditionals (Decompose Conditional, Replace with Polymorphism, Guard Clauses), Simplifying Method Calls (Introduce Parameter Object, Separate Query from Modifier), and Dealing with Generalization (Pull Up/Push Down, Extract Superclass/Interface).",
